23. Key Commands (EX280 Important)
Generate service certificate:
oc annotate service myservice \
service.beta.openshift.io/serving-cert-secret-name=mysecret
________________________________________
Check secret:
oc get secret
________________________________________
Create configmap:
oc create configmap ca-bundle
________________________________________
Inject CA bundle:
oc annotate configmap ca-bundle \
service.beta.openshift.io/inject-cabundle=true
________________________________________
Rotate certificate:
oc delete secret mysecret
