24. Key Exam Points
Remember these for EX280:
1️⃣ OpenShift encrypts control plane traffic automatically
2️⃣ Application traffic not encrypted by default
3️⃣ Service certificates generated by:
service-ca controller
4️⃣ Annotation for certificate:
service.beta.openshift.io/serving-cert-secret-name
5️⃣ TLS secret contains:
tls.crt
tls.key
6️⃣ CA bundle injected using:
service.beta.openshift.io/inject-cabundle=true

